    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work. The engine currently runs roughly with a persistent oil leak, and the transmission exhibits noticeable slipping between gears. Externally, there are several large dents and clear coat failure on the hood and roof, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional air conditioning. This car is ideal for a dedicated project or as a donor for parts, as it is not currently suitable for reliable daily use.",
